{"EpubVersion":2,"filepath":"","fixparentnode":"","floatingtheme":[],"folded":false,"markups":[{"date":"2025-03-23 21:08:23","docid":0,"id":2,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"光绪辛巳年（七年）六月二十三日 = 公历 1881年7月18日。马建忠和吴广霈皆因负有调查鸦片相关事情而路过越南。二人皆从天津出发。","page":243,"rect":[58.49999825656414,14.999999552965164,489.2499854490165,74.49999780952936],"type":11,"uuid":"79dde2313bda5658f882453552abb6ee"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:13:54","docid":0,"id":5,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"马建忠一行抵达西贡口外，时间是七月二十日，即公元1881年8月15日。","page":272,"rect":[62.99999812245369,38.999998837709484,585.9999825656419,71.49999789893636],"type":11,"uuid":"84b9ad39cbcb571f6a1a10a822025490"},{"CL":[103.49999691545972,583.4999826103455,106.12499683722862,756.9999768435962,106.12499683722862,776.9999768435962],"date":"2025-03-23 21:19:50","docid":0,"id":7,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"马建忠或许是和吴广霈一起同行，调查鸦片一事。这里又看到“张霈霖”。","page":272,"rect":[11.249999664723873,776.9999768435962,201.99999400973337,842.4999749213465],"type":9,"uuid":"46b8d930ffd08d75d4eb05800e1d414e"},{"CL":[510.7499847784643,119.99999642372143,472.87498590722726,100.2499976083637,472.87498590722726,80.2499976083637],"date":"2025-03-23 21:20:51","docid":0,"id":10,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"马建忠对于西贡整体的评价：人口众多，市容整洁。","page":273,"rect":[368.2499890252951,39.74999881535772,578.4999827891594,81.2499976083637],"type":9,"uuid":"8daff2f6065f6f04bb2902041539ebd8"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:21:18","docid":0,"id":12,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"张镜河","page":273,"rect":[530.249984197319,668.9999800622469,582.9999826550489,692.4999793916946],"type":11,"uuid":"46490152e06b074cdaad5611a83d40be"},{"CL":[172.49999485909953,113.99999660253535,377.4999881535772,14.999999552965175,397.4999881535772,14.999999552965175],"date":"2025-03-23 21:22:26","docid":0,"id":14,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"西贡动植物园。","page":273,"rect":[397.4999881535772,3.749999888241291,513.2499847337608,27.24999921768906],"type":9,"uuid":"7f9b5a5020156d4c4e95eae5c17a3245"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:27:06","docid":0,"id":15,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"马建忠、吴广霈二人奉命前往印度调查鸦片之事，中间途径包括西贡、新加坡在内的南洋各地。这两本游记或是为数不多的近代中国人赴印度游记。以越南部分而言，两人的游记存在着一定的差别：马建忠所记载较为简略，吴广霈所记较为详细。","page":273,"rect":[18.749999441206455,750.7499776259071,561.2499833032493,837.2499750778087],"type":11,"uuid":"c433ecbec8d27605ea2fe6891205b293"},{"CL":[86.24999742954977,290.2499913498762,184.87499449029576,88.24999796599155,184.87499449029576,68.24999796599155],"date":"2025-03-23 21:28:06","docid":0,"id":17,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"法国人准备进行铁路建设，马建忠的评价是“其志颇大”。吴广霈、马建忠二人对于法国人在越南的交通建设表示肯定。","page":273,"rect":[29.99999910593033,7.499999776482582,340.7499898746612,69.24999796599155],"type":9,"uuid":"a4ac9c9985dc51c7c8f958ee247c20e4"}],"maxid":17,"notelinks":[],"summaries":[],"title":"马建忠《 适可斋纪言纪行》","unimportant":[{"date":"2025-03-23 21:13:34","docid":0,"id":3,"imgfile":"dd291e42a9e65bf580c0bdfe3924d109.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":243,"rect":[406.4999878853563,94.49999718368062,398.9999881088737,715.499978676439],"type":1,"uuid":"42d1872bbc36bbb9cb0d24eccf29d95c"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:13:40","docid":0,"id":4,"imgfile":"80748fe21d77344f81709daccca4d146.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":272,"rect":[356.249989382923,99.74999702721843,356.99998936057125,195.74999416619556],"type":1,"uuid":"40c4561967cd3500769bb4dac88676e9"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:19:12","docid":0,"id":6,"imgfile":"699c83cf9ab95512e7f80d9e14844acb.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":272,"rect":[92.24999725073585,540.7499838843946,94.49999718368062,632.9999811351305],"type":1,"uuid":"551defa0b879156d57b45fc9d3344537"},{"date":"2025-03-23 21:20:22","docid":0,"id":8,"imgfile":"65861267e05853fdb73cc9d3474cc2b0.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":273,"rect"